It is necessary to stress one more point here. The discovery by these ç
sages that Brahman, the basis of the external universe and °tman, ç
the basis of the internal world, are ultimately one and arepure consciousness, ç
has obliterated the walls between these two fields of knowledge.
A brief account of the various sciences as developed in this country ç
